@startuml
title Frontend Observability (As-Is)
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho

actor User
node "Frontend App\nReact + Vite build" as FEApp
node "Nginx Static Host :80" as Nginx
node "Browser DevTools" as DevTools
node "Prometheus/Loki/Grafana Stack" as Obs

User -> FEApp : Su dung UI tren browser
FEApp -> Nginx : Serve static assets\n(index.html, js, css, tfjs model)
FEApp --> DevTools : console.error / network errors

note right of Obs
As-is:
- Chua co FE metrics endpoint
- Prometheus chua scrape FE
- Promtail stack hien tai chi map\nbackend/logs, chua map FE logs
end note

note right of Nginx
nginx.conf chi khai bao SPA fallback:\ntry_files $uri /index.html
end note

@enduml
